## Content Attribution

The content in the `content/` directory is scraped from Språkrådet (The Language
Council of Norway) at https://sprakradet.no/.

Språkrådet is a Norwegian government agency under the Ministry of Culture. Their
language guidance is produced as part of their public mandate under Språkloven
(the Norwegian Language Act).

Under Norwegian law (Åndsverkloven §9), works created by government agencies in
the exercise of public authority are generally not protected by copyright and
may be freely used.

Each content file includes a source URL (`Kilde:`) for attribution. When using
this content, please maintain proper attribution to Språkrådet as the original
source.

For questions about content reuse, contact Språkrådet at:
- Email: sporsmal@sprakradet.no
- Website: https://sprakradet.no/
